{"tid":2266044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"火車上大聲講電話，男子不滿遭勸反罵：我一個打你們全部！","createTime":"2020-11-01T03:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T04:38:19.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cdefa5442b2d0c48c7060175681a4b0b1ec924dd","tid":2266044,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmi8lx16iuA&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%B6%B2SETN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbmi8lx16iuA%26ab_channel%3D%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25B6%25B2SETN&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=9142e110\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmi8lx16iuA&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%B6%B2SETN</a><br />\n<br />\n今（31）日有民眾爆料，自己跟妻子日前一起搭火車前往宜蘭時，車廂內有位男子透過電話與人爭吵將近十分鐘，嚴重打擾到其他乘客。自己好聲勸阻這名男子，沒想到對方竟暴怒且全程脫下口罩，嗆聲要打架，過程中還不斷說「我一個打你們全部啦」等恐嚇言語，更威脅爆料民眾「小心一點」。"},{"pid":"b845dd3d4e6b0257a270d1fd97a7f090f0dbd3a5","tid":2266044,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">即刻落車</span>"},{"pid":"ce57fe2ec45ffff69280eff6b1c5ea3da8d08af2","tid":2266044,"uid":65638,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"台灣最美麗的風景是人"},{"pid":"7027a1dde3f61c8e2e9f8c06bc74e5ea71e95705","tid":2266044,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce57fe2ec45ffff69280eff6b1c5ea3da8d08af2","tid":2266044,"uid":65638,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"台灣最美麗的風景是人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQcLD04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQcLD04.jpg&h=00df7f98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"520